(TENANT HANDBOOK - OAKWOOD PROPERTY MANAGEMENT) Tj
T*
(Effective Date: January 1, 2026) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Section 1. Rent Payments) Tj
T*
(Rent is due on the 1st of each month. A grace period of five \(5\) calendar days is provided.) Tj
T*
(Payments received after the 5th incur a late fee equal to 5% of the monthly rent.) Tj
T*
(Accepted payment methods are ACH bank transfer and credit/debit card.) Tj
T*
(Cash payments are not accepted under any circumstances.) Tj
ET
endstream
endobj
