(Section 2. Security Deposits) Tj
T*
(Security deposits are equal to one \(1\) month of rent for one-year leases.) Tj
T*
(For leases longer than 12 months, a security deposit equal to two \(2\) months of rent is required.) Tj
T*
(Security deposits are returned within 30 days of lease termination, less any documented damages.) Tj
T*
(An itemized statement of deductions will be provided with any returned deposit.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Section 3. Maintenance Requests) Tj
T*
(Routine maintenance requests should be submitted through the tenant portal.) Tj
T*
(Emergency repairs \(water, gas, electrical, heat in winter\) must be reported via the 24-hour hotline.) Tj
T*
(Response time for emergencies is under 4 hours; routine requests are addressed within 3 business days.) Tj
ET
endstream
endobj
